      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为Education_StudentDB项目创建一个甘特图，重点展示包容结束日期的特性。标题就叫\"Inclusive end dates (Education_StudentDB)\"吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
