        "axisFormat",
        "%d",
        "inclusiveEndDates"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以日期格式是2019-01-01这种，坐标轴显示1、2、3这样的数字，并且结束日期是包含在内的。接下来任务部分怎么安排？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dateFormat",
        "axisFormat",
        "inclusiveEndDates"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "先建一个Section1区块，里面放两个任务对比。第一个叫\"2 Days\"，从2019-01-01开始，持续2天；第二个叫\"Manual Date\"，同样从2019-01-01开始，但手动指定结束日期到2019-01-03。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section",
        "Section1",
        "2 Days",
        "Manual Date",
        "2019-01-01",
        "2d",
        "2019-01-03"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我来画一下：区块Section1，任务1用持续天数2d，任务2直接写结束日期2019-01-03。这样两个任务应该能直观对比自动计算和手动指定结束日期的效果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Section1",
        "2 Days",
        "Manual Date",
        "2d",
        "2019-01-03"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "对，就是因为开了inclusiveEndDates，所以2天的任务实际上也会覆盖到1月2号，而手动指定的1月3号结束会包含当天。这样用户就能理解包容结束日期的行为了。",
      "elements_involved": [
